[[File:Wookiee_Chieftain.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A Wookiee Chieftain]]
A '''Wookiee Chieftain''', also known as a '''Wookiee Elder''', was a [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] with the ability to lead and to command troops on the battlefield, or managing a society of Wookiees. Chieftains also played roles in some government issues such as battles or war. Notably, they had the right to cancel the festivities of [[Life Day/Legends|Life Day]], the most important Wookiee [[holiday]].<ref name="TKD">"[[The Kashyyyk Depths]]"</ref> At the time of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], a council of venerated Elders accompanied Kashyyyk's [[Senator/Legends|representative]] to the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="IWTPM">''[[Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Episode I]]''</ref>

[[Merumeru/Legends|Merumeru]] was a Chieftain at the time of the [[Battle of Kashyyyk/Legends|Battle of Kashyyyk]] and, at 250 [[Standard year/Legends|years]] old, was one of the youngest to have held the title.<ref name="Merumeru">{{DB|character|merumeru|Merumeru}}</ref> About two decades later, during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the female Wookiee [[Ovarra]] acted as a Chieftain.<ref name="Rage">''[[Star Wars Galaxies: Rage of the Wookiees]]''</ref>

